body_html: TF members, I'm not sure I understand the tensorflowbutler comments, but it seems the issue creator is not responding to the request to drop requests for contributions. Can you fix this your end? It would suck for this issue to stall due to miscommunication/poor timing of interests. It is now 2 years old, but very important to those who care about it.
